				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Fear I found is a very useful spell. I am a level 10 enchanter and use this in conjunction with tashan to solo yellows with my pet. What I do is I pull with tashan, cast suffocating sphere on it, fear it, then have my pet and I chase after it. Once it unfears, I either suffocating sphere it then fear it again or just nuke it with chaotic feedback. This allows you to solo hard monsters and not get you or your pet killed.
